Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,記入這個表格里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,做的不是很好 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,萩生同學的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看響崇高的藝術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,主題是愛和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是把這個概念放大到極限的傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在最後的十分鐘真虧你趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小蓮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是獨具匠心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹能拿刀子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和繃帶一起綁在手上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要做到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我來餵你吧 小牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,花子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對我這種人你竟然如此關心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,迷你貓尾草 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太太太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我這個平時一直在添麻煩的人做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,二位真是像天使一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,響可不會做這種丟人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你把響當成什麼了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果蓮無論如何都要的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,說到夏令營我以為會是讓學生做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其實不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有點可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完飯之後就去入浴就寢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天請早點休息來消除疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是為了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要來枕頭大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,枕頭大戰是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在剩下最後一人為止用這個互相攻擊的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用這麼危險的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 會讓老師生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}我滾滾滾滾滾…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有怎麼用過被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,平常是睡床的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand Power
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 花子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,緞帶解不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我回想起在小雲雀家過夜的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也能和小雲雀一起睡 真是開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在夏令營的時候要把髮卡放在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽是這樣和我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,剛纔聽你們說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還一起過夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,響同學和蓮同學也是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,難得不會經常一起過夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然小時候經常會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,最近完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然早上經常會來叫我起床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,關係真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候不是經常一起過夜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有什麼不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,響可不會忘記 那些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要熄燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已經很久沒有這樣和蓮一起睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我吵醒你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 你睡不著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在大家一起 很興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是不習慣被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,握著手睡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,羊羊羊 貓尾！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快起來 小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想悠哉地睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,通告幸福班級全員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,五分鐘之內做好準備到正門集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到的人屁股要挨踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,總之趕快換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,眼鏡 眼鏡 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮你別誰回籠覺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,七個隊伍全員到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同學第一學期已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,除開一部分因病缺席的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分同學都參加了夏令營
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老師覺得非常高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{@\blur2\t(0,250,\blur0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs90\t(0,3500,0.05,\fs30)\bord0\c&H858585&\pos(630,85)\frx20\fry0\org(620.571,100)}箱庭 捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,進行幸福實訓「箱庭捉迷藏」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,箱庭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼由我和…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,還有我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,貓尾草！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,遊戲已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,來抓你們了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,手還會伸長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,萩生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,完全走散了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到底捉迷藏是什麼回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福班級的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這個箱庭捉迷藏是為積极參與的各位所準備的特別科目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,特別科目？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒出事的各位請確認下包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說來這裡面到底放了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,花子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀…piu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好大聲…piu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你還有空管我哦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是蓮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在找大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但不敵高溫和日照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只能像個青蟲一樣在樹木之間蠕動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蠕動簡直適合廢柴的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,先去找個沒人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去找一個既涼爽又適合睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不會被貓尾草和老師找到的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要去午睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,包裹突然被風颳走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,掛在了水車上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去取下來的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也掛上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點不好受不過這情景我見過！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是江戶時代的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那大概不是遊戲而是拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好像沒發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那個搞不好視野挺差的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在 走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我真沒有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有標記的卡片和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉和罐裝麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,500ml的礦泉水瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,手套 毛巾和望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有餐布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還有捉迷藏的規則說明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}還有笛子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,別吹 要被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,場地是被高牆隔離的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼藏都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同一房間的5人全部被抓住則宣告遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到遊戲截止的正午為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,根據被抓住的人數和時間來評分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個四葉草是我們的隊伍標識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,排名靠前的隊伍將在夏令營第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,入住套房並且可以吃到豪華山珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吊車尾的隊伍將獨自露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,並且食物自行解決
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我纔不要變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼響會在這種地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,完了 這下完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,睡在榻榻米上都睡不老實了還要露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小雲雀 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只要在中午之前不被抓到就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你這迷之自信從哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還有後續
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的木雕被放在了各處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,各自找到自己的木雕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,併成功匯合的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,會得到額外點數
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,找到木雕然後匯合…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡遲早也會被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有點擔心牡丹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起找木雕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,餓 走不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,說來今天沒吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得有香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Banana！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,總之這個先給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bana~na~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一根的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,星形標識的抓到一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這樣效率太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且視野又差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,編隊整齊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,選哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我又成包袱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,請放下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼來抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,蓮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不過總算是和瀑布說拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不想和雲雀丘她們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但為了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要找到蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,「願我嚐盡七苦八難」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}※ 戰國名將山中幸盛（山中鹿之助）的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福班同學們本身就揹負著不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要對這樣的她們降下試煉有些於心不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但這也是為了讓這些可悲的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠獲得真正的幸福
